---
import { Sparkles, Rocket, ArrowRight, CreditCard } from "lucide-astro";
---

<section class="py-12 bg-background-light dark:bg-background-dark">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-[2.5rem] bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800 p-8 md:p-12 shadow-sm grid-bg">
            
            <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-1/2 h-full bg-gradient-to-l from-primary/5 to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div>

            <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-5 lg:gap-10">
                
                <div class="lg:w-3/5 space-y-6">
                    <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-green-100 dark:bg-green-900/30 text-green-600 dark:text-green-400 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">
                        <Sparkles class="w-4 h-4" /> Oferta Plan Fundador
                    </span>
                    
                    <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-brand-blue dark:text-white leading-tight">
                        Comienza <span class="text-primary italic">gratis</span> y obtén tu <br class="hidden md:block"> tienda lista para vender 
                    </h2>
                    
                    <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 max-w-2xl">
                        Únete hoy mismo y activa tu ecosistema: <strong class="text-slate-900 dark:text-white">10 productos</strong> en catálogo, <strong class="text-slate-900 dark:text-white">pasarela segura</strong> plantillas profesionales para personalizarla con tu marca.
                    </p>

                    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-x-6 gap-y-2 text-sm font-bold text-slate-500">
                        <span class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary"></span> Sin costo por reserva</span>
                        <span class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-brand-blue"></span> Tardas menos de 5 min crearla</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="lg:w-2/5 flex flex-col items-center lg:items-end gap-4 w-full">
                    <a href="https://www.betogether.com.co/register" target="_blank" class="w-full md:w-auto bg-primary hover:bg-[#2900ff] !text-white font-black text-lg md:text-xl px-6 py-4 md:px-10 md:py-5 rounded-2xl shadow-xl shadow-primary/20 transition-all transform hover:scale-[1.03] active:scale-95 flex items-center justify-center gap-3 no-underline">
                        <Rocket class="w-5 h-5 md:w-6 md:h-6" />
                        EMPIEZA GRATIS
                        <ArrowRight class="w-4 h-4 md:w-5 h-5" />
                    </a>
                    
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-[#2900ff] font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-tighter">
                        <CreditCard class="w-4 h-4" />
                        No necesitas tarjeta de crédito
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .grid-bg {
        background-size: 50px 50px;
        background-image: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(230,0,126,0.05) 1px, transparent 1px), 
                          linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(230,0,126,0.05) 1px, transparent 1px);
    }
</style>